h4 #{Constants[Enums.Positions.STRIKER]}, #{Constants[Enums.Positions.JACK]} or #{Constants[Enums.Positions.KEEPER]} only
p
    | An attempt to #{Constants[Enums.Actions.PICK_UP]} must be made as a part of 
    | any action that moves a #{Constants[Enums.Positions.JACK]}, #{Constants[Enums.Positions.STRIKER]} 
    | or #{Constants[Enums.Positions.KEEPER]} onto a hex that contains the ball.
p
    | As part of a 
    a(href="/actions/#{Enums.Actions.SPRINT}") #{Constants[Enums.Actions.SPRINT]} 
    | action, the player must try
    | to #{Constants[Enums.Actions.PICK_UP]} before they change facing. As part of 
    | a 
    a(href="/actions/#{Enums.Actions.RUN}") #{Constants[Enums.Actions.RUN]} 
    | action, the player may face any direction 
    | before attempting to #{Constants[Enums.Actions.PICK_UP]}.

h5 #{Constants[Enums.Actions.PICK_UP]} is a 3 dice Skill test (1)
ul
    li +1 if the player is a #{Constants[Enums.Positions.STRIKER]}.
    li -1 if the player is a #{Constants[Enums.Positions.KEEPER]}.
    li -1 if this is part of a #{Constants[Enums.Actions.SPRINT]} action.
    li -1 per opposing player threatening the hex the player is in (maximum of -2).
table.table.table-striped
    tr
        td #{Constants[Enums.Actions.PICK_UP]} fails
        td The ball scatters and the rush ends.
    tr
        td #{Constants[Enums.Actions.PICK_UP]} succeeds
        td The player gains posession of the ball.
    tr
        td #{Constants[Enums.Actions.PICK_UP]} doubles
        td The player gains posession of the ball and takes an immediate free action.
p
    | Note that if a #{Constants[Enums.Positions.GUARD]} moves into a hex containing 
    | the ball, then the ball scatters immediately without ending the rush.
p
    | A player keeps the ball until they choose to 
    a(href="/actions/#{Enums.Actions.THROW}") #{Constants[Enums.Actions.THROW]} 
    | it, or until they ar knocked or fall down. If a player is knocked or falls 
    | down then the ball scatters in the direction they were facing from the hex 
    | they land in.
p
    | Holding the ball has no effect on a player's stats or available actions other 
    | than allowing them to make a #{Constants[Enums.Actions.THROW]} attempt.